<paragraph base="F16125508" id="IFRS11_27" principles="yes"><paranum>27</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 11"/><data name="paranum" value="27"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS11_P0076">In its <xref base="F37046511" href="../ias27/IAS27_4.dita#IAS27_4/IAS27_P0016">separate financial statements<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0345"/></ph></xref>, a party that participates in, but does not have <xref base="F16125581" href="IFRS11_APPA.dita#IFRS11_APPA/IFRS11_P0081">joint control<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0208"/></ph></xref> of, a <xref base="F16124095" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0019">joint arrangement<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0207"/></ph></xref> shall account for its interest in: </p><ol base="F16125510" id="IFRS11_L0004" type="lower-alpha"><li><li_value>(a)</li_value> <p base="F16125523" id="IFRS11_P0077">a <xref base="F16125582" href="IFRS11_APPA.dita#IFRS11_APPA/IFRS11_TE0003">joint operation<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0209"/></ph></xref> in accordance with <xref base="F16217380" href="IFRS11_23.dita#IFRS11_23" id="IFRS11_X0122">paragraph 23</xref>;</p></li><li><li_value>(b)</li_value> <p base="F16125526" id="IFRS11_P0078">a <xref base="F16125599" href="IFRS11_APPA.dita#IFRS11_APPA/IFRS11_P0084">joint venture<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0211"/></ph></xref> in accordance with <xref base="F68073777" href="../ifrs09/IFRS09_TOC.dita#IFRS09_TOC0001" id="IFRS11_X0123">IFRS 9</xref>, unless the entity has <xref base="F16124103" href="../ias28/IAS28_3.dita#IAS28_3/IAS28_P0023">significant influence<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0355"/></ph></xref> over the joint venture, in which case it shall apply <xref base="F16217399" href="../ias27/IAS27_10.dita#IAS27_10" id="IFRS11_X0124">paragraph 10 of IAS 27</xref> (as amended in 2011).</p></li></ol></body></paragraph>